  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Agent Brain系统画一个C4上下文图。这个系统的核心是一个Claude Code插件，能让开发者在IDE里用自然语言管理知识库。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ab",
        "plugin",
        "claude",
        "developer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以Claude Code是外部的AI助手，我们的插件是跑在它里面的？还是独立的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "claude",
        "plugin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Claude Code是外部系统，我们的插件是它的扩展。开发者先和Claude Code交互，然后通过斜杠命令触发我们的插件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "developer",
        "claude",
        "plugin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我把Developer画成Person，Claude Code画成System_Ext，然后用一条\"Uses\"关系连接，标注\"Interactive chat\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "developer",
        "claude"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。然后Claude Code通过斜杠命令调用我们的插件，这条关系应该是\"Invokes\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "claude",
        "plugin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Claude Code到Plugin的关系加上了。接下来插件内部是怎么分工的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "plugin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "插件本身不直接干活，它把命令委托给一个CLI工具。这个CLI是我们自己写的管理工具。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "plugin",
        "cli"
